# FlowSpace Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.

# AI Chat Agent: Configure via Settings UI or `npx flowspace setup`.
# LLM provider settings are saved to ~/Library/Application Support/FlowSpace/.llm-settings.json
# No environment variables needed for LLM configuration.

# Google auth is handled by the gws CLI — no Google credentials needed here.
# Run `npx flowspace setup` to configure Google OAuth.
